  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A piece of paper lives in a small town where it rains all year round. Every day when it comes home from work, it uses an umbrella to resist splashing water from all over. It really hates the rain. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192360/extras/cce0acd98f0f6033e961b40dfe14e86c.avif?t=1758426810\" width=150 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Experience rainy days in a world of hand drawn style </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Super cute character </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Immersive music that fits the atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Experience the protagonist's changing attitude towards rainy days</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TO FACE THE RAIN!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The duration of the game is about 30 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game feedback QQ group: 992719842</p>",
